WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Important art deserves
more than ownership.

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:11.500
It deserves stewardship.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.500
Art Investment Group Trust exists
to acquire, hold, and care for works

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:24.000
of cultural significance within
a disciplined, governed framework.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.500
We operate with institutional standards,
long horizon ownership,

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:33.000
and uncompromising custody and care.

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:40.000
Our focus is not speculation.

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:47.500
It is preservation, legitimacy,
and legacy.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.500
Art Investment Group Trust.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
The Art that Matters.

00:00:56.500 --> 00:01:00.000
